      <p style="font-size: 0.9rem; margin: 0.5rem 0 0;">Each year's zodiac animal dominates New Year decorations and cards</p>
    </div>
    <div style="background: #f0f9ff; padding: 1.2rem; border-radius: 8px; text-align: center;">
      <div style="font-size: 1.8rem;">🗣️</div>
      <strong>Conversation Topic</strong>
      <p style="font-size: 0.9rem; margin: 0.5rem 0 0;">何年？(nan-doshi?) is a common question — "What's your zodiac?"</p>
    </div>
    <div style="background: #f0fdf4; padding: 1.2rem; border-radius: 8px; text-align: center;">
      <div style="font-size: 1.8rem;">📚</div>
      <strong>Kanji Practice</strong>
      <p style="font-size: 0.9rem; margin: 0.5rem 0 0;">12 animal kanji are practical vocabulary for learners</p>
